21#include <ctype.h>
22#include "mpc-impl.h"
23
24int
25mpc_set_str (mpc_t z, const char *str, int base, mpc_rnd_t rnd)
26{
27 char *p;
28 int inex;
29
30 inex = mpc_strtoc (z, str, &p, base, rnd);
31
32 if (inex != -1){
33 while (isspace ((unsigned char) (*p)))
34 p++;
35 if (*p == '\0')
36 return inex;
37 }
38
39 mpfr_set_nan (mpc_realref (z));
40 mpfr_set_nan (mpc_imagref (z));
41 return -1;
42}
